            "stanza_text": "Dans mon délire je revois\nCes longs fleuves bordés de vignes\nOù les flots à la douce voix\nCharmaient les lauriers et les cygnes,"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 5,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 17,
                    "line_text": "Et je cherche l'horizon pur",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 18,
                    "line_text": "Où, dans leurs graves symétries,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 19,
                    "line_text": "Blanchissaient, éclairant l'azur,",
